# Internal Language Model

See [INTERNAL_LANGUAGE_MODEL.md](../../INTERNAL_LANGUAGE_MODEL.md).

## Rules

1. Source of truth: `aipify-core/knowledge/internal-language-model/function-vocabulary.txt`
2. Programmatic vocabulary: `lib/internal-language-model/vocabulary.ts`
3. Never describe Aipify as replacing employees or running the company alone.
4. Use preferred wording from `FUNCTION_VOCABULARY` when explaining features.
5. Chat: `detectAipifyFeatureIntent()` for feature and replacement questions.
6. Core philosophy: augment people — humans decide, Aipify informs and prepares.
